            "answer_text": "Read. Read all kinds of books, in different genres, published over a long span of time. As you read, pay attention to what the author was trying to share with you. Look up unfamiliar words to expand your vocabulary. Write. Try to write in different styles, emulating different authors\u2019 rhythms and patterns. If you begin by emulating other authors, you will discover your own voice. Use correct spelling and grammar. Always. ",
